{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_0129SxtpMFA4XKdrUF3UEUv1","type":"tool_result","content":"/home/kazuki/public_html/spec-anchor/.spec-anchor\n/home/kazuki/public_html/spec-anchor/spec_anchor/templates/.spec-anchor\n/home/kazuki/public_html/spec-anchor/doc/e2eテストCODEX実施用/evidence/20260523-002300-codex-e2e-slash-skill/tmp/slash-skill-project/.spec-anchor\n/home/kazuki/public_html/spec-anchor/doc/e2eテストCODEX実施用/evidence/20260523-000315-codex-e2e-additional/tmp/setup-codex-only/.spec-anchor\n/home/kazuki/public_html/spec-anchor/doc/e2eテストCODEX実施用/evidence/20260523-000315-codex-e2e-additional/tmp/failed-required-artifact/.spec-anchor\n/home/kazuki/public_html/spec-anchor/doc/e2eテストCODEX実施用/evidence/20260523-000315-codex-e2e-additional/tmp/watch-options/.spec-anchor\n/home/kazuki/public_html/spec-anchor/doc/e2eテストCODEX実施用/evidence/20260523-000315-codex-e2e-additional/tmp/watcher-running-gate/.spec-anchor\n/home/kazuki/public_html/spec-anchor/doc/e2eテストCODEX実施用/evidence/20260523-000315-codex-e2e-additional/tmp/setup-no-init/.spec-anchor\n/home/kazuki/public_html/spec-anchor/doc/e2eテストCODEX実施用/evidence/20260523-000315-codex-e2e-additional/tmp/concept-missing/.spec-anchor\n/home/kazuki/public_html/spec-anchor/doc/e2eテストCODEX実施用/evidence/20260523-000315-codex-e2e-additional/tmp/qdrant-missing-fallback/.spec-anchor\n/home/kazuki/public_html/spec-anchor/doc/e2eテストCODEX実施用/evidence/20260523-000315-codex-e2e-additional/tmp/parent-config-project/.spec-anchor\n/home/kazuki/public_html/spec-anchor/doc/e2eテストCODEX実施用/evidence/20260523-000315-codex-e2e-additional/tmp/pending-conflict-gate/.spec-anchor\n/home/kazuki/public_html/spec-anchor/doc/e2eテストCODEX実施用/evidence/20260523-000315-codex-e2e-additional/tmp/setup-claude-only/.spec-anchor\n/home/kazuki/public_html/spec-anchor/doc/e2eテストCODEX実施用/evidence/20260523-001153-codex-e2e-f001-retest/tmp/f001-clean-project/.spec-anchor\n/home/kazuki/public_html/spec-anchor/doc/e2eテストCODEX実施用/evidence/202605