{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-sonnet-4-6","id":"msg_01D3yqxPPo4yDRjNNSV7ybK9","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"I need to find the spec-anchor configuration for the ec-spoke.local project. Let me check if there's a spec-anchor setup at the ec-spoke.local project root, and also look for any auth-specific documents.\n\nThe ec-spoke.local project doesn't seem to have a .spec-anchor directory. Let me check in more detail.\n\nAlso, the user asked about \"認証セッションとCSRFの仕様\" - I need to find the specific spec files. Let me look at doc04 (未決定事項) and any auth-related docs.","signature":""}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"stop_details":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":6445,"cache_read_input_tokens":33482,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":6445},"output_tokens":9,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"diagnostics":null,"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"c5976bea-db53-4952-a093-280a919f4f68","uuid":"1b42427a-7f33-49b6-9d19-ccb0fb9ceae5","request_id":"req_011CbHrNJjgx3Mq6mUiNVNUW"}
